{"lemma":"بُلُوغٌ","slug":"بُلُوغٌ","root":"ب.ل.غ","root_slug":"ب-ل-غ","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ل-غ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3222"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%BA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of بَلَغَ (balaḡa, “to reach”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"reaching, attaining","examples":[{"text":"بُلُوغُ قِمَّةِ إِڤِرِسْت لَيْسَ بِالْأَمْرِ السَّهْل.","english":"Reaching Mount Everest is not an easy thing."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"puberty, maturity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"full age, majority"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"execution, accomplishment, completion"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3222","headword_ar":"بُلُوغٌ","root":"blg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibolaAgN","text_ar":"اـِبْلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ablg","text_ar":"ابلغ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", but it seems that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AblAg","text_ar":"ابلاغ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgN","text_ar":"بَلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buluwgN","text_ar":"بُلُوغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and this observation will be found to be confirmed by a statement immediately following this sentence,] signify The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reaching, attaining, arriving at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming to, the utmost point of that to which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towards which, one tends"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"betakes himself, to which one directs his course,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which one seeks, pursues, endeavours to reach, desires, intends,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposes; whether it be a place, or a time, or any affair or state or event that is meditated or intended or determined or appointed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being at the point thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says Abu-1-Kásim in the Mufradát. (TA: [in which it is said, in the supplement to the present art., that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgN","text_ar":"بَلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reaching, attaining, arriving at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming to, a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"]) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga AlmakaAna","text_ar":"بَلَغَ المَكَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almanozila","text_ar":"المَنْزِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buluwgN","text_ar":"بُلُوغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgN","text_ar":"بَلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as shown above],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He reached, attained, arrived at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place of abode:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and (so in the S, but in the K “ or, ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was, or became, at the point of reaching it, attaining it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (S, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fabalagona A^ajalahuna","text_ar":"فَبَلَغْنَ اَجَلَهُنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [ii. 232], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they have fully attained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ended, their term."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) But"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_i*aA balagona A^ajalahun~a","text_ar":"فَاـِذَا بَلَغْنَ اَجَلَهُنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the same [lxv. 2], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And when they are near to attaining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ending, their term:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are at the point of accomplishing their term."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA.) It has the first of the meanings explained above in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga A^a$ud~ahu","text_ar":"بَلَغَ اَشُدَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[Kur xii. 22 &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained his manly vigour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full maturity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) And in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balagaA^arobaEiyna sanapF","text_ar":"بَلَغَاَرْبَعِينَ سَنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"[Kur xlvii. 14,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained"},{"kind":"text","text":"the age of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forty years"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga maEahu Als~aEoYa","text_ar":"بَلَغَ مَعَهُ السَّعْىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[Kur xxxvii. 100,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained to working with him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) In the Kur [iii. 35], occurs the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqado balaganiYa Alkibaru","text_ar":"وَقَدْ بَلَغَنِىَ الكِبَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When old age hath come to me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overtaken me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and in another place [xix. 9],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa qado balagotu mina Alkibari Eutiy~FA","text_ar":"وَ قَدْ بَلَغْتُ مِنَ الكِبَرِ عُتِيًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And I have reached the extreme degree of old age:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so explained in the Expos. of the Jel]: phrases like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adorakaniYa Aljahodu","text_ar":"اَدْرَكَنِىَ الجَهْدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adorakotuhu","text_ar":"اَدْرَكْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Er-Rághib, TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA balaga","text_ar":"مَا بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lazimahu *`lika baAligFA","text_ar":"لَزِمَهُ ذٰلِكَ بَالِغًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"with the accus. case as a denotative of state; meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That clave to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adhered to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rising to its highest degree"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almanozila","text_ar":"المَنْزِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained above. (Msb.) [But"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA balaga","text_ar":"مَا بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAligFA","text_ar":"بَالِغًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"more frequently means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whatever point, degree, amount, sum, quantity, number,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, it may reach, attain, arrive at, come to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amount to."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga fulaAnN mabolagahu","text_ar":"بَلَغَ فُلَانٌ مَبْلَغَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mabolagatuhu","text_ar":"مَبْلَغَتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one reached,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attained, his utmost point"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scope"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"degree"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga fiY AlEilomi AlmabaAliga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ فِى العِلْمِ المَبَالِغَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained, in knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"science, the utmost degrees of proficiency"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga fiY","text_ar":"بَلَغَ فِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljawodapi mabolagFA","text_ar":"الجَوْدَةِ مَبْلَغًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It reached a consummate degree in goodness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K, * TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga mina Aljawodapi","text_ar":"بَلَغَ مِنَ الجَوْدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mabolagFA","text_ar":"مَبْلَغًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained a consummate degree of goodliness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: said of a boy that has attained to puberty. (O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga gaAyatahu fiY AlT~alabi","text_ar":"بَلَغَ غَايَتَهُ فِى الطَّلَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did his utmost,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used his utmost power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability, in seeking to attain an object"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhd","text_ar":"جهد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga A^aqoSaY majohuwdi baEiyrihi fiY Als~ayori","text_ar":"بَلَغَ اَقْصَى مَجْهُودِ بَعِيرِهِ فِى السَّيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exerted the utmost endeavour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"effort,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength, of his camel, in journeying"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nkv","text_ar":"نكث"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga jahoda daAb~atihi","text_ar":"بَلَغَ جَهْدَ دَابَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahadahaA","text_ar":"جَهَدَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He jaded, harassed, distressed, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wearied, his beast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhd","text_ar":"جهد"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga ma$aq~atahu","text_ar":"بَلَغَ مَشَقَّتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga minohu Alma$aq~apa","text_ar":"بَلَغَ مِنْهُ المَشَقَّةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahadahu","text_ar":"جَهَدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a Ealayohi","text_ar":"شَقَّ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, jaded him, harassed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ditressed him, afflicted him, oppressed him, overpowered him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus in each of these instances, as in many similar cases, the verb with the inf. n. that follows is equivalent to the verb of that inf. n.]. (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jhd","text_ar":"جهد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [And, elliptically,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga minohu","text_ar":"بَلَغَ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga minohu Alm$aq~apa","text_ar":"بَلَغَ مِنْهُ المشَقَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained above: and often meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had, an effect upon him; it affected him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"frequently said of wine and the like: and of a saying; as in the Ksh and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":251},{"kind":"text","text":"Bd in iv. 66, where"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yabolugu minohumo","text_ar":"يَبْلُغُ مِنْهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wayuw^aviru fiyhi","text_ar":"وَيُوَثِرُ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as an explicative: see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baliygN","text_ar":"بَلِيغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balagota min~aA Albulagiyna","text_ar":"بَلَغْتَ مِنَّا البُلَغِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albilagiyna","text_ar":"البِلَغِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~a","text_ar":"كُلَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mabolagK","text_ar":"مَبْلَغٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albulagiyna","text_ar":"البُلَغِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below. And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balagotu mina","text_ar":"بَلَغْتُ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amori Alma$aq~apa","text_ar":"الاَمْرِ المَشَقَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I experienced distress from the affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"event"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mD","text_ar":"مض"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [See also an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibidN","text_ar":"اـِبِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaganiY","text_ar":"بَلَغَنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It has come to my knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"been related to me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"been told me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it came to my knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: and in this case it is generally followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^an~a","text_ar":"اَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano","text_ar":"اَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^an~a","text_ar":"اَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": for exs., see these two particles. And in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaganiY Eanohu","text_ar":"بَلَغَنِى عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Information has come to me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"information came to me, from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concerning him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"that such a thing has happened, or had happened.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a letter or writing, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgN","text_ar":"بَلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buluwgN","text_ar":"بُلُوغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It reached, arrived,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And said of a plant, or of herbage,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It attained its full growth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and of a tree, such as a palm-tree &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its fruit became ripe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, TA:) and of fruit,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became ripe."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) Also, said of a boy, (T, S, M, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buluwgN","text_ar":"بُلُوغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or, as IKoot says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgN","text_ar":"بَلَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He attained to puberty, virility, ripeness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"maturity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoraka","text_ar":"اَدْرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotalama","text_ar":"اِحْتَلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, Msb;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attained a consummate degree of goodliness"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga mina Aljawodapi mabolagFA","text_ar":"بَلَغَ مِنَ الجَوْدَةِ مَبْلَغًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (O, TA:) as though he attained the time of the writing of his marriage-contract, and of his having duties or obligations imposed upon him: (TA:) and in like manner one says of a girl,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balagato","text_ar":"بَلَغَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga A@ll~`hu bihi","text_ar":"بَلَغَ ا@للّٰهُ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God caused him to reach, attain, arrive at,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"come to, his appointed end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"term of life;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajalahu","text_ar":"اَجَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or the like, being understood]. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga A@ll~`hu bika A^akolaA^a AlEumuri","text_ar":"بَلَغَ ا@للّٰهُ بِكَ اَكْلَاَ العُمُرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God cause thee to reach,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the extreme,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most distant, period of life!"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"klA^","text_ar":"كلا"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalotu bihi maA balaga bihi","text_ar":"فَعَلْتُ بِهِ مَا بَلَغَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^a*aY wa Almakoruwho","text_ar":"الاَذَى وَ المَكْرُوهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did with him that which caused him to come to what was annoying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurtful, and evil"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga bihi Albilagiyna","text_ar":"بَلَغَ بِهِ البِلَغِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see the last word of this phrase below. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buliga","text_ar":"بُلِغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuniYa","text_ar":"عُنِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, jaded, harasssed, distressed, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wearied."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baluga","text_ar":"بَلُغَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgapN","text_ar":"بَلَاغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baliyg","text_ar":"بَلِيغ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSiyH","text_ar":"فَصِيح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[more properly signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chaste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perspicuous, in speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but here meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eloquent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, * Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"penetrating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"effective, in tongue;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attaining, by his speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diction, the utmost scope of his mind and desire."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) The difference between"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAgapN","text_ar":"بَلَاغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faSaAHapN","text_ar":"فَصَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is this: that the latter is an attribute of a single word and of speech and of the speaker; but the former is an attribute only of speech and the speaker: (Kull:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blAgp","text_ar":"بلاغة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the speaker is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A faculty whereby one is enabled to compose language suitable to the exigency of the case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the occasion of speaking"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or writing"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with chasteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perspicuity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eloquence, thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in language, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suitableness to the exigency of the case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the occasion of speaking"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"writing"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with chasteness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perspicuity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eloquence, thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KT.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb","TA","AHn","T","O","Kull"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}